In banking, your compensation is generally a function of (1) your performan=
ce, (2) your group=E2=80=99s performance and (3) your bank=E2=80=99s perfor=
mance. Credit Suisse=E2=80=99s=C2=A0overall=C2=A0performance, right now, is=
