UBS for, roughly, nothing. That is an environment in which it is hard to ge=
t paid, both as an economic matter and also as a political matter; the Swis=
s government has   ordered Credit Suisse to freeze some pay. There are some=
 reasonable ideas of collective responsibility there, but of course lots of=
 Credit Suisse=C2=A0 traders and wealth managers=C2=A0were=C2=A0making a lo=
t of money for the bank, and their best chance of getting paid is somewhere=
