</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Oh I think the SEC thinks it is exactly where =
it needs to be.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Anyway the celebrity stuff is straightforward:=
</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The SEC thinks Tron's tokens are secur=
ities.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You might think =E2=80=94=
