<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That=E2=80=99s because the bank=E2=80=99s tang=
ible book value is far underwater, according to Wall Street analysts, creat=
ing a capital gap of as much as $13.5 billion =E2=80=94 a sum that may help=
