mscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !i=
mportant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bo=
ttom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  don=E2=80=99t all have to go =
down with the ship</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Wall Street banks and European rivals are undo=
ing de facto hiring freezes after Credit Suisse Group AG=E2=80=99s emergenc=
y rescue by UBS Group AG, unable to resist the lure of top talent available=
 at a discount.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Firms such as Deutsche Bank AG, Citigroup Inc.=
 and JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co. are readying to hire some of the Swiss firm=
=E2=80=99s investment bankers and wealth managers, people with knowledge of=
 the matter said. Conversations are beginning in New York and London, and s=
ome headhunters are even flying to Zurich for meetings, the people said.</p=
>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">While shockwaves from Credit Suisse=E2=80=99s =
effective collapse are still reverberating across markets, in some banks th=
e narrative has shifted from contagion to the once-in-a-decade opportunitie=
s on offer. The first emergency sale of a major bank since the financial cr=
isis is presenting rivals the chance to scoop up key personnel or businesse=
s that might otherwise not have been on offer.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In banking, your compensation is generally a f=
unction of (1) your performance, (2) your group=E2=80=99s performance and (=
3) your bank=E2=80=99s performance. Credit Suisse=E2=80=99s=C2=A0<em>overal=
l=C2=A0</em>performance, right now, is about as bad as possible; it was res=
cued by Swiss authorities and sold to UBS for, roughly, nothing. That is an=
 environment in which it is hard to get paid, both as an economic matter an=
d also as a political matter; the Swiss government has <a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/30935281.265435/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb2=
1iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMjEvY3JlZGl0LXN1aXNzZS1lbXBsb3llZ=
